### Register
POST http://localhost:8000/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "user1@habitquest.dev",
  "password": "StrongPass123!"
}

### Login
POST http://localhost:8000/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "user1@habitquest.dev",
  "password": "StrongPass123!"
}

### List quests (replace token)
GET http://localhost:8000/api/quests
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Validate quest
POST http://localhost:8000/api/quests/1/validate
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "comment": "Quete terminee"
}

### Admin create quest template
POST http://localhost:8000/api/admin/quest-templates
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "kind": "daily",
  "title": "10 min de lecture",
  "description": "Lire 10 minutes minimum",
  "xpReward": 50,
  "isActive": true
}

### Admin create event
POST http://localhost:8000/api/admin/events
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "startsAt": "2026-04-01T08:00:00+00:00",
  "endsAt": "2026-04-08T08:00:00+00:00",
  "questTemplateIds": [1, 2]
}
